			<h2>Join us on Sunday</h2>
			<p class="meeting">10:30am | 2165 Park St.</p>
			<p>Our gatherings take place in Riverside, which is just west of downtown Jacksonville. We currently meet in The Jr. League building, two blocks west of historic Five Points.</p>
