			<h2>What to expect</h2>
			<p>On Sundays, we gather collectively as a church to worship Jesus and for discipleship by hearing about Jesus from the bible, worshipping Jesus through song and giving, and serving one another through community and prayer.</p>
			<h2>For the kids</h2>
			<p>We provide a safe, fun place for children from 0 to 4 years old. They'll play a little, have a little snack, and learn about the Bible. <em>(Don't forget to ask them about what they learned.)</em></p>
